headline: FUJIFILM Q3 Earnings & Revenues Up Y/Y, FY25 View Revised

headline: Fortive (FTV) Is Up 13.4% After Strong Q4, Upbeat 2026 EPS Outlook And Buybacks - Has The Bull Case Changed?
summary: In early February 2026, Fortive reported fourth-quarter 2025 results with sales of US$1,122.5 million, adjusted EPS of US$0.90, and full-year sales of US$4,159.1 million, while also executing substantial share repurchases under its ongoing buyback programs.
